WITH RankedMovies AS (
    SELECT 
        a.id AS movie_id,
        a.title AS movie_title,
        a.production_year,
        a.kind_id,
        COUNT(ci.person_id) AS num_cast_members,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT ak.name, ', ') AS all_aka_names
    FROM 
        aka_title a
    LEFT JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON ci.movie_id = a.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        aka_name ak ON ak.person_id = ci.person_id
    GROUP BY 
        a.id, a.title, a.production_year, a.kind_id
),
MovieDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        rm.movie_id,
        rm.movie_title,
        rm.production_year,
        rt.role AS leading_role,
        COUNT(mc.company_id) AS production_companies,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ', ') AS movie_keywords
    FROM 
        RankedMovies rm
    LEFT JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON cc.movie_id = rm.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        role_type rt ON rt.id = cc.status_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_companies mc ON mc.movie_id = rm.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON mk.movie_id = rm.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        keyword k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id
    GROUP BY 
        rm.movie_id, rm.movie_title, rm.production_year, rt.role
),
FinalOutput AS (
    SELECT 
        md.movie_id,
        md.movie_title,
        md.production_year,
        md.leading_role,
        md.production_companies,
        md.movie_keywords,
        rm.num_cast_members,
        rm.all_aka_names
    FROM 
        MovieDetails md
    JOIN 
        RankedMovies rm ON md.movie_id = rm.movie_id
)
SELECT 
    movie_id,
    movie_title,
    production_year,
    leading_role,
    production_companies,
    num_cast_members,
    movie_keywords,
    all_aka_names
FROM 
    FinalOutput
ORDER BY 
    production_year DESC, 
    num_cast_members DESC

FROM (SELECT "t2"."MOVIE_ID", "t2"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", MIN("role_type"."role") AS "LEADING_ROLE", COUNT("movie_companies"."company_id") AS "PRODUCTION_COMPANIES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "MOVIE_KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", MIN("aka_title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "aka_title"."kind_id" AS "KIND_ID", COUNT("cast_info"."person_id") AS "NUM_CAST_MEMBERS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name0"."name", ', ') AS "ALL_AKA_NAMES"
FROM "aka_title"
LEFT JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_title"."movie_id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "aka_name" AS "aka_name0" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name0"."person_id"
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year", "aka_title"."kind_id") AS "t2"
LEFT JOIN "complete_cast" ON "t2"."MOVIE_ID" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "role_type" ON "complete_cast"."status_id" = "role_type"."id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t2"."MOVIE_ID" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "t2"."MOVIE_ID" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."MOVIE_ID", "t2"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "role_type"."role") AS "t5"
INNER JOIN (SELECT MIN("aka_title0"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", MIN("aka_title0"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title0"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "aka_title0"."kind_id" AS "KIND_ID", COUNT("cast_info0"."person_id") AS "NUM_CAST_MEMBERS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "s1"."name", ', ') AS "ALL_AKA_NAMES"
FROM "aka_title" AS "aka_title0"
LEFT JOIN "cast_info" AS "cast_info0" ON "aka_title0"."movie_id" = "cast_info0"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info0"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
GROUP BY "aka_title0"."id", "aka_title0"."title", "aka_title0"."production_year", "aka_title0"."kind_id") AS "t8" ON "t5"."MOVIE_ID" = "t8"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t8"."NUM_CAST_MEMBERS" DESC NULLS FIRST
